            // Plan 91.12 (2026-06-01, D126 retract): WriteBuffer and ReadBuffer
            // removed ‚Äî now Nova-defined records over `[]u8` primitives
            // (std/runtime/{write,read}_buffer.nv). emit_type_decl must emit
